How to build a Maven project?

Steps file-->new--> Other...>Maven...>Maven project....>>Next....>
Create simple project...> Use default location....>Group ID...>Artifact ID...> Finish..



Then Updates propertise file if needed
<properties>
<maven.compiler.target>17</maven.compiler.target>
<maven.compiler.source>17</maven.compiler.source>
</properties>


